*** 7.4.2.5 Islamic Response
Political obligations derive from ummah membership and divine guidance, requiring social responsibility and Islamic brotherhood according to Islamic political framework.

*** 7.4.2.6 Hindu Response
Political obligations derive from dharmic duty and social harmony, requiring contextual responsibility and righteous governance according to Hindu political philosophy.

*** 7.4.2.7 Buddhist Response
Political obligations derive from interdependence and compassionate wisdom, requiring social engagement and liberation from suffering according to Buddhist political ethics.

*** 7.4.2.8 Confucian Response
